abstracts.cdata!:
In order to help the country make better
            use of domestic and external resources for the development
            of its economy, a credit of SDR 23.8 million will finance
            this proposed TA project. The objectives of this credit are
            fourfold. First, the credit will: (a) provide foreign
            exchange for TA required for project preparation,
            implementation and for studies required for the formulation
            of economic and sector policies. It will also; (b) assist in
            improving the capacity of Government agencies to prepare and
            implement development projects; and (c) improve the
            management and coordination of TA within Government
            agencies. Finally, the credit will; (d) encourage the
            strengthening of the local consulting industry. The project
            will finance high priority technical assistance and training subprojects.
